defaultThis submission addresses the constitutional role of the judiciary within the UK
default 
defaultconstitution
default and the choices available to the courts – in their vindication of the rule of law – when fa
defaultced with ‘unconstitutional’ legislation. It 
defaultdraws on arguments and analysis published 
defaultin
