default2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultI
defaultn the absence of a codified constitution guaranteeing its status
default 
defaultthe role
default and powers
default of the judiciary
default in 
defaultthe
default UK
default constitution 
defaulthave traditionally
default had to be inferred or induced from particular judicial decisions
